They just want us to tell them
what is the best strategy for

00:00:35.820 --> 00:00:37.080
solving the problem.

00:00:37.080 --> 00:00:39.380
So the first choice they say,
finding an equation

00:00:39.380 --> 00:00:40.470
for the blue line.

00:00:40.470 --> 00:00:43.100
So let's look at this graph that
they've also given us.

00:00:43.100 --> 00:00:47.330
So the blue line here is the
graph using the information

00:00:47.330 --> 00:00:50.430
