than the amount Ben earned.

00:01:16.010 --> 00:01:18.310
So that's the equation of
that line right there.

00:01:18.310 --> 00:01:21.270
Well, that by itself isn't going
to help you figure out

00:01:21.270 --> 00:01:22.610
how much did each earn.

00:01:22.610 --> 00:01:25.390
So that by itself won't
solve the problem.

00:01:25.390 --> 00:01:27.560
Finding the red line's
y-intercept.

00:01:27.560 --> 00:01:28.540
So let's look at the red line.

00:01:28.540 --> 00:01:31.810
The red line C. is using the
information that Abby and Ben

00:01:31.810 --> 00:01:33.510
