00:01:33.510 --> 00:01:35.600
It's this information up here.

00:01:35.600 --> 00:01:39.230
And the equation of that would
be Abby's earnings plus Ben's

00:01:39.230 --> 00:01:41.980
earnings are equal to $50.

00:01:41.980 --> 00:01:44.065
If you were to just find
the y-intercept there,

00:01:44.065 --> 00:01:44.780
it's just at 50.

00:01:44.780 --> 00:01:47.370
That's really not giving you
any information in figuring

00:01:47.370 --> 00:01:49.360
out how much did they each
earn and actually

00:01:49.360 --> 00:01:50.950
