00:02:35.000 --> 00:02:35.830
That works.

00:02:35.830 --> 00:02:39.750
If Abby earns 30 and Ben earns
20, they'll earn $50.

00:02:39.750 --> 00:02:43.550
And 30 is $10 more than 20.

00:02:43.550 --> 00:02:44.250
So this worked.

